                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-08-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 5, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay instructs Mr. Rockhill to endeavor to have flour retained on the free
                    list, if possible.)</p>
            </div>
